
'''欧洲证券及市场管理局''' 是一个[[欧洲联盟|欧洲联盟]]金融监管机构<ref>{{cite web |url=http://europa.eu/rapid/pressReleasesAction.do?reference=MEMO/11/1&format=HTML&aged=0&language=EN&guiLanguage=enn |title=EUROPA – Press Releases – A turning point for the European financial sector |publisher=Europa.eu |date=1 January 2011 |accessdate=24 April 2011 |archive-date=2020-03-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200314011340/https://ec.europa.eu/commission/presscorner/detail/en/MEMO_11_1 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 设在巴黎。

ESMA<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.esma.europa.eu |title=ESMA |publisher=Esma.europa.eu |date=1 January 2011 |accessdate=24 April 2011 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6ARueH63F?url=http://www.esma.europa.eu/ |archivedate=2012年9月5日 }}</ref> 2011年1月1日取代[[欧洲证券监管委员会|欧洲证券监管委员会]]（欧洲证监会）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.esma.europa.eu/popup2.php?id=7331 |title=[ESMA] – Document |publisher=Esma.europa.eu |date= |accessdate=24 April 2011 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110720161724/http://www.esma.europa.eu/popup2.php?id=7331 |archivedate=2011年7月20日 }}</ref>这是[[欧洲金融监管体系|欧洲金融监管体系]]三个新的欧洲监管当局(ESAs)之一 另外两个是[[欧洲银行管理局|EBA]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.eba.europa.eu |title=European Banking Authority – EBA – Home |publisher=Eba.europa.eu |date= |accessdate=24 April 2011 |archive-date=2011-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110310155000/http://www.eba.europa.eu/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>和[[欧洲保险和职业养老金管理局|EIOPA]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.eiopa.europa.eu |title=EIOPA: Home |publisher=Eiopa.europa.eu |date= |accessdate=24 April 2011 |archive-date=2019-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190630053837/https://eiopa.europa.eu/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

==简介== 
改进[[金融市场|金融市场]]在欧洲的运作,加强[[投资者保护|投资者保护]]和国家主管当局合作。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.esma.europa.eu/index.php?page=cesrinshort&mac=0&id= |title=ESMA [European Securities and Markets Authority] |publisher=Esma.europa.eu |date= |accessdate=24 April 2011 |archive-date=2011-05-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110502172642/http://www.esma.europa.eu/index.php?page=cesrinshort&mac=0&id= |dead-url=no }}</ref>  

